HEADWORD: Nitriary
<hw>Ni"tri*a*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Niter</er>.]</ety> <def>An artificial bed of animal matter for the
manufacture of niter by nitrification. See <er>Nitrification</er>,
2.</def>⟦br⟧
